  "detailed_description": "Single player game with puzzle elements and survival in a mysterious building, where you are chased by a mad attraction - Toothy Jack, who serves Hostess. Use Toy Gun to solve puzzles and move forward<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/0c9a23cb76bf62046d86b97a764c2ba7.poster.avif?t=1772538482\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/0c9a23cb76bf62046d86b97a764c2ba7.webm?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/0c9a23cb76bf62046d86b97a764c2ba7.mp4?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Using the ToyGun is not so easy, you need to calculate the distance to the target and the speed of the projectile. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/f5b8091ffe46d480f349b3fa413537bf.poster.avif?t=1772538482\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/f5b8091ffe46d480f349b3fa413537bf.webm?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/f5b8091ffe46d480f349b3fa413537bf.mp4?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take cover, move cautiously along the narrow path, trying not to fall into the abyss, visiting strange rooms and memory-lost creatures. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/e5976b6fd24ba53f9d08b3d0594de606.poster.avif?t=1772538482\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/e5976b6fd24ba53f9d08b3d0594de606.webm?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/e5976b6fd24ba53f9d08b3d0594de606.mp4?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Don’t let Toothy Jack see you! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/2915632388a083a187d6170f7c611d4e.poster.avif?t=1772538482\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/2915632388a083a187d6170f7c611d4e.webm?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/2915632388a083a187d6170f7c611d4e.mp4?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The old amusement test room is full of secrets and dangers. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/3342c280f6bea220f9bedda1b42bad40.poster.avif?t=1772538482\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/3342c280f6bea220f9bedda1b42bad40.webm?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643470/extras/3342c280f6bea220f9bedda1b42bad40.mp4?t=1772538482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"Toothy Jack will bring you back. To the Hostess, to the Hostess... \"",
